Description:
    Create component directory(if not exists) and widget files.
    If wj_widgets.yaml file aready exists, this generator add
    a new widget entry into that file(not override other widget
    entries) so that you can answer 'Y' when asked 'overwrite
    components/<component_name>/_db/init/wj_widgets.yml?'.

WjWidgetName:
    Fully qualified widget name (<component_name>/<widget_name> format)

WidgetIcon:
    The widget icon is copied to public/components/<component_name>/images/<widget_name>.png
    This file is copy of 'exec.png' (32x32) file originated from Crystal Project.
    You can replace it for your original widget icon, a PNG file of 32x32 size.

Example:
    ./script/generate wj_widget blog/widget


